reviews.text: Food is great, atmosphere and staff is just what you expect from the Mong Kok district.  Overall a positive experience.
Very average food quality, service was above average in terms of Hong Kong standard.

I went here to Yum Cha in Sunday morning. The dim sum were usual and no signature. Maybe they are many restaurants under the same group, it can be imagined most of the dim sum are came from central kitchen. 

However, the waitresses were awfully. They pretended no seeing anyone who put up his or her hands. We couldn't clarify which waitress to add hot water, which one who would clean up the table. We often heard that 'this is not my job, you ask someone else ". 

If good service with acceptable food quality, we can give many allowance. However, whatever how good of the food quality, wont go again for such service.
The service is pretty good ,the food is fine.
Good food reasonably priced

result.name: 旺角好彩海鮮酒家

reviews.text: 食材錯
生客坐低十分鐘都冇人招呼 ， 伙記各自各 ， 河水不犯井水。  伙記服務一般， 熟客就招呼

原本一家人想食飯慶祝生日，早一星期book位（房），當時話無房，要到時睇下有就幫我地轉。

去到當晚.....竟然話無位話我地無book！  當晚有人擺酒，搞乜，都唔知溝通上出咩問题，雖然個經理幫手睇有無位幫我地開張大枱，但搞左好耐，擺好哂位又唔叫我地過去，我地見到又要我地出聲。  佢地啲譚仔知客真係幾難溝通下。

早知落樓下京華酒樓好過，又平啲。

呢度我諗應該無下次。食飯最緊要開心。 呢度嘅野食，價錢等都唔再需要評論了。
非常熱鬧的粤菜餐廳！食物的價錢相對便宜，份量也可以，味道稍為一般但不差｡
唔錯幾好、中意去那裡飲早茶和食晚鈑。👍😋
